def is_food_egg(item: item):

behavior boil_the_egg(egg: item, pot: item, stove: item):
    body:
        bind water_source: item where:
            is_sink(water_source)
        # Fill pot with water

        achieve is_on(stove)

            is_stove(stove)
        # Find a stove
